! Inline code

Single backtick `let x = 1`, and double backtick to embed a literal backtick:
``text with a ` backtick inside``.

! Fenced code blocks

Each fenced block is highlighted by its language plugin (when installed).

```javascript
function add(a, b) {
	const sum = a + b;
	return sum; // line comment
}
```

```python
def greet(name="World"):
	return f"Hello, {name}!"
```

