! Typed blocks

Typed blocks declare their content type after `$$$`:

$$$text/css
.foo { color: red; }
$$$

$$$application/javascript
const answer = 42;
$$$

$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki
This is ''wikitext'' inside a typed block, with a [[Link]] and <<currentTiddler>>.
$$$
